track_notes: This route came to me once again from John G4YSS. It is almost 20 Km return and a full day exercise. I used a bike as the tracks are very good for riding on a hybrid bike. Suggest if you bike up you lock her up at NY 829243 and walk to the AZ from there. You will need to push the bike on the short section up to High Crag and then ride the rest of the way to NZ 829243.
track_title: G/NP-002 Mickle Fell from Grains of the Beck (B6276 road)
